 businesses said raj date managing partner of fenway summer llc  our mortgage business together with ethos is a terrific first example – a technologyenabled business that will deliver great products to otherwise underserved customers  ethos lending anticipates beginning to originate agency mortgages in the nd quarter of   by the end of the year ethos plans to be one of the first wholesale originators of nonqualified mortgages  ethos will offer affordable and accessible mortgage products that are unavailable in the market today such as interestonly loans under the current conforming balance threshold of  the companys management team described in greater detail below is drawn from fenway summer and ethos lending llc     raj date founder of fenway summer and former deputy director of the consumer financial protection bureau cfpb will serve as the chairman of the board of ethos lending   mark lefanowicz who has been serving as ceo of fenway summer mortgage will serve as ceo of ethos lending  earlier in his career mr lefanowicz was cfo of provident funding and ceo of eloan adam carmel the founder of ethos lending llc will serve as president of ethos lending  prior to founding ethos mr carmel was an executive vice president at provident funding where he managed servicing and subservicing operations  kin chung will be chief credit officer of ethos lending mr chung joined fenway summer after holding senior analytics positions at a variety of leading financial firms including fannie mae and capital one  he holds a phd in mathematics from princeton university erik stern will be chief operating officer of ethos lending  mr stern has deep experience in mortgage loan underwriting funding servicing and most other operational aspects of the mortgage wholesale business  mr stern held numerous management positions at provident funding sean souther will be chief information officer of ethos lending  mr souther has experience in developing unique and cuttingedge technology solutions in the mortgage business  mr souther has held senior management technology positions at fidelity national lending and lender processing services  chris haspel will lead capital markets for ethos lending  mr haspel has deep capital markets experience including time in leadership positions at the cfpb ginnie mae capital one blackrock financial management and ge capital mortgage mitch hochberg will serve as the general counsel of ethos lending  prior to joining fenway summer mr hochberg was a senior counsel within the cfpb office of regulations  he spent several years at cadwalader wichersham  taft llp where he was responsible for managing several significant litigations relating to mortgage loan underwriting servicing and securitization  i had the opportunity to work with adam earlier in my career he is a savvy and disciplined operator and a great fit with our team  we are very excited about our companys unique ability to offer both agency eligible and nonqualifying mortgages to the mortgage broker community said mr lefanowicz ethos has been hard at work building an efficient and scalable mortgage platform mr carmel said combining our collective core competencies is an exciting opportunity and i am delighted to be partnering with fenway summer about fenway summer fenway summer llc is a hybrid advisory and venture investment firm focused on us consumer finance for more information about fenway summer llc visit wwwfenwaysummercom  media contact sean omealia fenway summer  seanomealiafenwaysummercom news distributed by pr newswire ireach httpsireachprnewswirecom source fenway summer related links httpwwwfenwaysummercom  categories money business tags banking  financial services residential real estate acquisitions mergers and takeovers venture capital personnel announcements more roth ceo adam roth recognized on staffing industry analysts  under  posted on  shoppers looking for a new car can experience easy financing at performance kia posted on  landmark global research 